CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Small Fry! - In the groove is this sax player at the Alpha picnic.  Left to right: Charles Matthews, Kansas City, Mo.; Harry Abels, and Jackie and Beverly Butler."
TitMainTitle: Charles Matthews, Harry Abels, and Jackie and Beverly Butler, watching saxophone player at Alpha Phi Alpha picnic
